      "instruction": "<p>Line a <strong>loaf tin</strong> (23 x13 x7cm) with <strong>non-stick baking paper</strong> and grease with <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>veggie loaf</strong> <strong>mixture</strong> to the prepared tin, pressing down into the corners and smoothing the top over with a spatula</p><p>Put the tin in the oven for 40 min or until browned and firm in the middle, reserve the pan – this is your <strong>squash loaf</strong></p><p>Tip: If you don't have a loaf tin, shape into a log instead!</p>",
